{"tid":1612724,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我做緊HR 有個cand講左樣政府爆野俾我地知","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:16:54.000Z","uid":84817,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89fb66eacb7d0f0e8ef6cc7221a407f3d725405b","tid":1612724,"uid":84817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"話說有個男仔嚟我地公司in Executive Assistant<br />\n都係廿幾歲仔 讀本地大學<br />\n傾傾下佢話佢自己係政府做緊普通clerk<br />\n本身考左政府EO 過晒啲筆試面試<br />\n但最後冇做 (心諗EO entry 都30k啦點解會揀我地份20k嚟做)<br />\n再問落去<br />\n原來佢話因為過唔到&quot;背景查核&quot;<br />\n政府出左offical 信俾佢話fail左個查核<br />\n佢仲話佢所有報既同學朋友都過唔到...<br />\n其實去到呢到都諗到咩原因啦...<br />\n但佢加多一句:我識政府啲大粒同我講 呢一批EO 既candidate pool<br />\n所有local U 都唔揀<br />\n只揀外國大學回流既人<br />\n咁大家明咩事啦"},{"pid":"9e7b6a4c225014e47c8f5eb61bfa670996a645e0","tid":1612724,"uid":84817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"政府擺明唔想我地呢一代人入去<br />\n一個都唔要"},{"pid":"94f0711e407bedfaf2a91b60b7f6f6c733b125d5","tid":1612724,"uid":52041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"外國回流唔係仲衰咩"},{"pid":"77c26b7cc4caac90e5691dd30ebd5601a1f16cff","tid":1612724,"uid":223216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94f0711e407bedfaf2a91b60b7f6f6c733b125d5","tid":1612724,"uid":52041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"外國回流唔係仲衰咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:45:53.000Z","msg":"無係香港生活既離地撚"},{"pid":"a208db6913783e1e18ca3b7f7f2d983b6f50f74c","tid":1612724,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ef6432d69bc31c43f355933fde46bdf94825b0c","tid":1612724,"uid":311714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"解散警隊<br />\n下一步係要重組政府"},{"pid":"a0b6f0ce3eef34067f726fe2a53d46ee49028c33","tid":1612724,"uid":156582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94f0711e407bedfaf2a91b